name: NFTSEA Tickets by NFT Access & Transient Labs

metadata.name: NFTSEA IPIC Theater
metadata.description:
NFTSEA is a first-of-its-kind takeover of IPIC Fulton Market on June 20 from 6PM-12AM- a luxury 8 screen Movie Theatre at The Seaport. Join us for Live Music, Live Twitter Spaces, short film premieres, a speakeasy, collector & artist spotlights, and cocktails custom curated by an expert mixologist.  

These are commemorative tickets only and do not guarantee access into the event.
